{"name":"葛西記念財団","short_name":"葛西記念財団","description":"葛西記念財団は、葛西氏にまつわる歴史・文化・人物・地域の記録を調査・保存・発信し、次の世代へ継承する活動団体です。","start_url":"./","scope":"./","display":"standalone","background_color":"#fffdf9","theme_color":"#312e81","lang":"ja","dir":"ltr","icons":[{"src":"assets/icon-192.png","sizes":"192x192","type":"image/png"},{"src":"assets/icon-512.png","sizes":"512x512","type":"image/png"}]}